20:39.433 --> 20:40.298
- Hey, Lily.
- Hello, Simanyin.

20:40.300 --> 20:42.234
(slurred gibberish)

20:42.236 --> 20:43.235
(mocking sounds)

20:43.237 --> 20:44.936
Oh, I got to knock
on the door first.

20:44.938 --> 20:46.204
Oh.
(laughs)

20:46.206 --> 20:48.039
Something equally at home
on a midnight stroll

20:48.041 --> 20:49.541
or during the horizontal mambo.

20:49.543 --> 20:50.508
On the Fertile Crescent.

20:50.510 --> 20:51.509
- Or doing the Bone Dance.
- Oh.

20:51.511 --> 20:52.911
♪ ♪

20:52.913 --> 20:55.814
♪ You can do anything ♪

20:55.816 --> 20:57.248
♪ You can... ♪

20:57.250 --> 20:59.384
Oh, I hope those are your keys.

20:59.386 --> 21:01.152
(laughter)
